Why don't we move away from here?

00:02:22.710 --> 00:02:25.910
Okay. Well, we have a mortgage,
so it's a bit hard,

00:02:26.310 --> 00:02:29.510
but if we rent out the flat,
we can get some money,

00:02:30.790 --> 00:02:32.190
but under this situation...

00:02:32.390 --> 00:02:38.320
What will happen to the person
l wrote on my piece of paper later?

00:02:40.160 --> 00:02:42.860
I can't search anything
if we move away.

00:02:43.620 --> 00:02:47.180
Let's save moving away as
our last resort.

00:02:48.260 --> 00:02:49.140
Why?

00:02:50.220 --> 00:02:51.900
Because l mentioned money again?

00:02:52.460 --> 00:02:54.140
Sorry, but we'll be okay.

00:02:54.300 --> 00:02:56.860
I think we should move away
even if it'll be tough.

00:02:57.820 --> 00:03:02.420
I'm scared, but the police will come
to investigate this for a while,

00:03:03.260 --> 00:03:05.620
so maybe l feel safest here.

00:03:06.340 --> 00:03:09.540
What? But l am scared!

00:03:10.420 --> 00:03:11.780
Don't cry.

00:03:14.060 --> 00:03:15.660
Nana, go to bed with me.

00:03:17.420 --> 00:03:20.500
Sorry, l'll send
a business email first.

00:03:21.620 --> 00:03:22.580
At a time like this?

00:03:22.740 --> 00:03:25.580
I'll send an email to ask
if they can extend the deadline.

