Ryo Kakinuma,

00:05:36.190 --> 00:05:37.310
Airi Seno.

00:05:37.630 --> 00:05:38.510
203's...

00:05:38.710 --> 00:05:39.590
Sorry.

00:05:40.630 --> 00:05:42.590
203's Xinyi Lin,

00:05:43.030 --> 00:05:45.390
204's Jun Nishimura,

00:05:45.590 --> 00:05:47.630
301's Mikiha Ono

00:05:48.070 --> 00:05:49.950
and the flat next door,

00:05:50.110 --> 00:05:51.350
501's Go Sano.

00:05:51.630 --> 00:05:53.190
Why are the photos like that?

00:05:53.270 --> 00:05:55.350
They were taken secretly
during the interview.

