They are 201's Airi Seno,

00:06:06.180 --> 00:06:07.660
202's Sawa Kuroshima,

00:06:08.260 --> 00:06:10.260
203's Iqbal Bin Dato,

00:06:10.940 --> 00:06:12.460
302's Nana Tezuka,

00:06:13.180 --> 00:06:14.980
404's Yuki Etou.

00:06:15.100 --> 00:06:17.040
We found these people's
fingerprints.

00:06:17.120 --> 00:06:19.540
The one who left fingerprints
in the flat

00:06:20.060 --> 00:06:21.900
and has no alibi is...

00:06:22.420 --> 00:06:23.540
This girl?

00:06:25.350 --> 00:06:27.230
- I'm counting on you!
- Yes, sir...

00:06:32.070 --> 00:06:33.910
Hey, take this with you.

00:06:34.270 --> 00:06:35.630
What? lt's salt again?

00:06:35.710 --> 00:06:37.550
The residential tower is cursed!

00:06:39.110 --> 00:06:40.030
Indeed.

00:06:42.110 --> 00:06:45.550
The property manager killed himself
last month,

00:06:45.750 --> 00:06:48.270
a diner exploded and the owner died,

00:06:48.390 --> 00:06:49.420
the waitress...

00:06:49.820 --> 00:06:52.300
and a regular customer live there.

00:06:52.620 --> 00:06:56.870
On top of that, the customer found
the body of the murder victims.

00:06:57.230 --> 00:07:02.300
Hey, speaking of which, why didn't
you report these just now?

00:07:03.900 --> 00:07:05.270
Do you remember Mr Enomoto?

00:07:05.750 --> 00:07:07.340
- Mr Kamiya.
- Yes?

00:07:08.540 --> 00:07:09.460
Good evening.

00:07:09.740 --> 00:07:11.820
Enomoto lives there too. And?

00:07:12.100 --> 00:07:15.070
He indirectly put pressure on me.

00:07:15.910 --> 00:07:17.030
Enomoto?

00:07:19.790 --> 00:07:20.630
Hey.

00:07:22.150 --> 00:07:25.670
He seems to want to be promoted
one rank up from lnspector,

00:07:25.830 --> 00:07:27.470
so he cares about his reputation.

00:07:27.830 --> 00:07:31.030
Whether he can be a Superintendent,
the boss's appraisal matters.

00:07:31.270 --> 00:07:33.710
So about what happened
at the residential tower...

00:07:33.990 --> 00:07:38.650
Nowadays, you never know
what will be against your favour.

00:07:39.530 --> 00:07:41.790
Well, l don't need to hide anything,

00:07:42.070 --> 00:07:43.830
but don't you think
you don't need

00:07:43.910 --> 00:07:46.310
to make connections between
everything and make a fuss?

00:07:46.390 --> 00:07:47.230
What?

00:07:47.310 --> 00:07:50.550
Just because he happens to live
in the condo that a murder happened?

00:07:50.710 --> 00:07:52.550
It won't affect his promotion!

00:07:52.710 --> 00:07:54.790
That's what l said too, but...

00:07:55.030 --> 00:07:56.630
Well, this isn't important,

00:07:57.630 --> 00:08:01.190
but the Deputy Chief
is waiting for my promotion.

00:08:03.790 --> 00:08:08.030
If officers of his faction
are at the best possible positions,

00:08:08.310 --> 00:08:10.590
it's easier for him to work too.

00:08:13.510 --> 00:08:14.830
At a time like this,

00:08:15.430 --> 00:08:19.830
if my chance of being promoted
is lost because of you guys,

00:08:20.190 --> 00:08:23.670
what will the Deputy Chief think?

00:08:24.110 --> 00:08:28.150
In that case, do as Enomoto wishes.

00:08:28.630 --> 00:08:29.470
What?

00:08:29.550 --> 00:08:32.110
Idiot! lf you get dragged
into an organisation's trouble,

00:08:32.310 --> 00:08:34.110
it'll be even scarier than a curse.

00:08:36.230 --> 00:08:38.270
Alibi not verified</i>

00:08:38.350 --> 00:08:41.350
Room 203, Xinyi Lin</i>

